      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, an ER visit? that seems a bit much right? i dont have any pain or anything, its just quiet. i think it's probably just some wax or air pressure or something. u think i could just try some ear drops or maybe do the valsalva maneuver (the thing where you pinch your nose and blow) to see if it pops back to normal first? like, how much time do i actually have before it's \"permanent\"?",
